<template class="bg-secondary">
  
  
    
    {{ thing}}








</template>

<script>

  import {stuffService} from '@/_services'
  
   
  export default {
  
  name: 'stuffFetch',
  
  data(){

    return {
        

             thing:[0]

    }
  },

     mounted() {

       stuffService.getAllstuff()
                                .then(res=>{

                                  console.log(res.data.data)

                                  this.thing= res.data.data

                                })
                                  .catch(err=>{console.log(err)})
   
    
    }
        
   
          }
           
            
             
        
          


        
</script>
